snippet.title: Nicole Balian
snippet.description:
Hello Everyone! 

I'm Nicole and I love to be creative. 
My channel consists of 3D Printing, Painting, digital design and my journey as a creative entrepreneur. I hope you enjoy my videos as much as I enjoyed filming them. 

Please like and subscribe! ♡
